  add: item => {
    updateField(current => [...current, item]);
  },
  remove: id => {
    updateField(current => current.filter(i => i.id !== id));
  },
};
```

**Why:**

- Centralized state management
- Type-safe updates
- Reactive - components re-render automatically
- Service logic separated from UI

